### Reading

The student is resposible for reading the assigned material. A reading
schedule is provided with the class schedule on the course website.


### Assignments

There will be a project due almost every week during the
semester. Projects are designed to take 10+ hours of work for
successful completion. These assignments will involve various
activities to promote a deeper understanding of the course
materials. Most of the projects build upon previous work, so
students who fall behind will not be able to complete the course
successfully.


